&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/MandarinOrientalHotelGroup.png&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-9215&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/MandarinOrientalHotelGroup.png&quot; alt=&quot;MandarinOrientalHotelGroup&quot; width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take refuge at Mandarin Oriental Hotel Group and discover some of the most exquisite hotels and resorts in the world. &nbsp;Unwind at a meditative spa, indulge in the finest dining or recharge in a culturally-vibrant capital. Each destination brings celebrated comfort and legendary service. Whether you&amp;#8217;re longing for the indulgence of a poolside retreat, the bustle of a major metropolis or the relaxation of a world-class spa, Mandarin Oriental hotels and resorts offer that perfect retreat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Stunningly designed and beautifully appointed, Mandarin Oriental, Las Vegas is a Forbes triple 5-star luxury hotel at the heart of The Strip. With views of the city and the desert, we offer the perfect mix of style, serenity and luxury.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Diners Club cardmembers enjoy&nbsp;extra special recognition throughout their stay with valuable benefits including:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Upgrade upon availability (room to room, suite to suite)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Welcome amenity &ndash; seasonal amenities that vary throughout the year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continental breakfast for two on each morning during the stay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complimentary Internet access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;USD50 dining or spa service credit for Suite reservations only (one-time per stay)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Early check-in, based on availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reserve your room &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mandarinoriental.com/lasvegas/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;online&lt;/a&gt;,&nbsp;call Mandarin Oriental Central Reservations&nbsp;or call the hotel directly. When booking, enter&nbsp;code &amp;#8220;&lt;strong&gt;DINCLB&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#8221; in the &amp;#8216;Corporate/Promo Code&amp;#8217; field or provide the code to a phone agent.&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.mandarinoriental.com/dci&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Click here&lt;/a&gt; for or more information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer is subject to availability, blackout dates may apply and advance booking is required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer is valid on select room categories and is not valid for group bookings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other offers or promotions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

